6.0.4
==========================

 * Added: More triggers API for integration
 * Added: Better browser compatibility as of 2025
 * Added: Template schema, allowing users to create their own themes/templates
 * Added: Removed certain JS/CSS dependencies
 * Added: Improved UI/UX
 * Added: Smart caching when saving
 * Added: Flexible configuration on host page
 * Added: More hooks, allowing potential integration (document updated)
 * Added: Certain components like menu bar, attribute panels are fully configurable
 * Added: Better interaction and UI effects
 * Added: More publishing options
 * Added: Allow users to export/import development bundle
 * Added: More compact HTML generated
 * Added: Improved performance in general
 * Fixed: HTML corrupt in certain cases
 * Fixed: Cannot import existing page design, due to incompatible components
 * Fixed: UTF-8 encoding issues
 * Fixed: Inconsistent HTML output for the same page design
 * Fixed: Various template import issues
